Summary of significant modifications made by the "onChange by Sairo"
fork (see ATTRIBUTION.md for the full changelog and commit history):

  * Rebranded the user interface to "onChange by Sairo"; the upstream
    name and logos are used only for attribution.
  * Introduced a new brand design system (see DESIGN.md) and replaced
    the colour palette, typography, and layout tokens.
  * Added: Watch Templates library, Scheduled Digest emails, AI-assisted
    Filter Builder (natural-language → CSS/XPath suggestion).
  * Security hardening: non-root Docker user, scoped CORS, pooled HTTP
    sessions, chardet confidence gate, transient-HTTP retry, was_edited
    consumption fix, XSS fix in client-side modal dialog, ARIA/mobile
    accessibility pass.
  * Frontend: deferred script loading, console-log gating,
    mobile tap-target breakpoint.

